ater-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="DIIV - “沸水中的青蛙”专辑插图。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/DIIV-Frog-in-Boiling-Water-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/DIIV-Frog-in-Boiling-Water-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/DIIV-Frog-in-Boiling-Water-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/DIIV-Frog-in-Boiling-Water-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/DIIV-Frog-in-Boiling-Water-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/DIIV-Frog-in-Boiling-Water-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/DIIV-Frog-in-Boiling-Water-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3593192" class="wp-caption-text"> DIIV –“沸水中的青蛙”专辑插图。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>他们继续说道：“我们理解这个比喻是关于末期资本主义社会缓慢、病态、极其平庸的崩溃，我们可能已经开始接受这种残酷的现实。那是沸水，我们是青蛙。这张专辑或多或少是从我们现代状况的各个角度拍摄的快照集，我们认为它突出了这种崩溃的样子，更具体地说，突出了它的感觉。”</p><p>在其他地方，DIIV 还宣布了一系列美国、英国和欧盟巡演日期。下个月，乐队将穿越欧洲和英国，在荷兰、德国、瑞士、法国、英国和爱尔兰停留。从那里，乐队将于六月开始他们的美国巡演，并在旧金山、圣克鲁斯、西雅图、达拉斯、圣安东尼奥、洛杉矶、费城、奥兰多、迈阿密和布鲁克林等主要城市停留。</p><p>门票预售将于当地时间明天 2 月 27 日上午 10 点开始。一般门票销售将于当地时间 3 月 1 日星期五上午 10 点开始。查看下面的完整日期列表，并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fdiiv-tickets%2Fartist%2F1751796" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处获取英国门票</a>和<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fdiiv-tickets%2Fartist%2F1751796" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处获取美国门票。</a></p><h2> <strong>DIIV 2024 英国、美国和欧盟巡演日期为：</strong></h2><p><strong>行进</strong><br /><strong>5 – 蒂沃利弗里登堡 – 荷兰乌得勒支</strong><br /><stro